:::Obsidian:::

::a small transport pod fell from the sky.  Inside it was one of the greatest 
Cybertronian military leaders ever: Obsidian.  He crashed to the earth near 
Destructor's base(if that is where KitKat's Predacons are) and opens up a 
comm::
Obsidian:  I am Obsidian.  If you are Predacons, i would like to join you.  
Do you accept?
